# Copy to .dev.vars for local `pnpm dev` / `./run.sh`. NEVER commit .dev.vars.
#
# TURNSTILE_SECRET pairing:
#   - If your local wrangler.toml uses the always-pass TEST site key
#     (1x00000000000000000000AA), keep the test secret below as-is.
#   - If your local wrangler.toml uses your REAL Turnstile site key
#     (same one you ship to production), paste your REAL secret here too
#     and add `localhost` to the Turnstile site's allowed domains so the
#     widget issues tokens that verify. A real site key paired with the
#     test secret always 400s on verify.
SESSION_SECRET="change-me-to-a-long-random-string-at-least-32-bytes"
RESEND_API_KEY="re_xxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxx"
TURNSTILE_SECRET="1x0000000000000000000000000000000AA"
IP_HASH_SALT="change-me-rotate-periodically"
